{"tid":2496870,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"楊千嬅同仔仔一齊隔離素顏自拍　加埋濾鏡仍然難掩疲態","createTime":"2021-04-20T06:24:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T06:47:58.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"db5a948361b3585860aa4466ca27966f74c9b84c","tid":2496870,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T06:24:19.000Z","msg":"楊千嬅同老公返內地拍攝綜藝節目拍攝，連仔仔丁進諾（Torres）亦都同行。不過喺開工前夕，三人需要先接受接受隔離。不過，唔知係未因為要照顧仔仔關係，楊千嬅幾次喺小紅書分享隔離生活時，都顯得十分疲乏。<br />\n<br />\n千嬅上載第一條小紅書影片時，雖然已經有妝兼且使用了美顏效果，但雙眼卻略嫌無神，其後千嬅再拍第二條片，明顯精神不少，她在影片本分享推介書本。而日前千嬅以「做家務」為題拍攝影片時，疲相再次出現，但佢似乎唔多介意，仲好認真介紹帶備嘅煮食材料及用具，又透露影片由Torres操刀，千嬅透露隔離期間，可以同Torres有更多聊天機會，但最希望嘅係仔仔可以煮嘢比佢食。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210419/460906292534317056981764.jpeg/jgNAjK2DUVo3TaBkcm9jqsECOiyUAnuMRslv_UbJb_0?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210419%2F460906292534317056981764.jpeg%2FjgNAjK2DUVo3TaBkcm9jqsECOiyUAnuMRslv_UbJb_0%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=789d44d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210419/460905927663423488758391.jpeg/1l4xE_U1AIf6aprPT5vpkF3dfhEFIDI2vjL-bb4y_m0?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210419%2F460905927663423488758391.jpeg%2F1l4xE_U1AIf6aprPT5vpkF3dfhEFIDI2vjL-bb4y_m0%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=7e80e11c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210419/460906294614953984389426.jpeg/N6jL895Vu0dTzLC77hEJRz-Ltnt5l5BBZX-DlWV_g5U?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210419%2F460906294614953984389426.jpeg%2FN6jL895Vu0dTzLC77hEJRz-Ltnt5l5BBZX-DlWV_g5U%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=679c61e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5dbf9f5a8cebeeb62baddc3a0984251acc374c1d","tid":2496870,"uid":19437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T06:25:31.000Z","msg":"人一藍樣便<img src=\"/